instructions: On your Android phone and tablet, go to Google.com or open the Google app . If you haven t already, sign in to your Google Account. Search for an image. Tap the image you want to add. Tap Add to .
On your Android phone or tablet, go to images.google.com or open the Google app . Search for an image. Touch and hold the image. Tap Share .
On your Android phone or tablet, go to images.google.com or open the Google app . Search for an image. Tap the image. A larger version opens. Touch and hold the image. Tap Download image .
